  "method": [
    "Take a saucepan and heat oil over the medium heat.",
    "Put garlic and onion and cook for 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add chipotle adobo sauce, tomato sauce, and chicken broth, and bring",
    "it to boil.",
    "Put cilantro in it and turn down the heat.",
    "Add diced tomatoes, oregano, drained beans, cumin, corn, and stir.",
    "Put chicken breasts, and cook for 5-6 hours on the low heat.",
    "Shred the chicken and put it back to the soup.",
    "Add cumin and salt to taste.",
    "Pour in bowls and put avocado, cheese, cilantro, sour cream, tortilla",
    "chips, and scallions. Enjoy!"
